Interface LogProperty.PropertyGetter<T>

Type Parameters:
T - value type.
All Known Subinterfaces:
LogProperty.PropertyGetter.ChildPropertyGetter<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
LogProperty.PropertyGetter.RootPropertyGetter
Enclosing interface:
LogProperty
public static sealed interface LogProperty.PropertyGetter<T> permits LogProperty.PropertyGetter.RootPropertyGetter, LogProperty.PropertyGetter.ChildPropertyGetter<T>
Extracts and converts from LogProperties and is also an immutable builder for LogProperty.Propertys.

    LogProperty.PropertyGetter.RootPropertyGetter
    A property getter and builder that has no conversion but may prefix the key and search recursively up the key path.
